  "body": "> \ud83e\udd16 This PR was written by Coder Agent on behalf of Danielle Maywood \ud83e\udd16\n\nTwo fixes for flaky Chromatic visual tests:\n\n**Scroll stories** \u2014 All 6 `AgentChatPageView` scroll stories (`ScrollToBottomButton`, `ScrollPositionPreservedOnNewContent`, `ScrollPinnedToBottomOnNewContent`, `ScrollNotJumpedDuringTouch`, `ScrollNotJumpedDuringWheel`, `ScrollRepinnedAfterWheelDeferredAppend`) now have `chromatic: { disableSnapshot: true }`. These stories test scroll behavior via play functions and produce non-deterministic snapshots.\n\n**Calendar stories** \u2014 Added `defaultMonth` and `today` props to all Calendar stories so the displayed month and today-highlight are pinned to `2025-03-15` instead of drifting with the real date.",
  "changed_files": 2,
